articles.title: Giant flying insect found on Walmart building turns out to be Jurassic-era find - CNN
articles.description: A winged insect found on the side of a big-box store has been identified as the rare Jurassic-era giant lacewing. While the insect used to be widespread in eastern North America, this sighting is the first one since the 1950s.
